attributes.name: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 atmos Undermycar Pepper
attributes.story: Japan’s atmos teams up with South Korean brand Undermycar on the ASICS GEL Kayano 14 ‘Pepper Black,’ featuring a dark olive mesh upper with grey synthetic overlays and black side stripes. ASICS branding adorns the tongue and sockliner, while a decorative metal plate marked with Undermycar and atmos logos can be attached to the upper eyelet. The lifestyle runner sits atop a lightweight EVA midsole with visible GEL cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Unaffected Infinite Wonders Pack Green
attributes.story: Dropping as part of the collaborative ‘Infinite Wonders Pack,’ the UNAFFECTED x ASICS GEL Kayano 14 ‘Posy Green’ celebrates the 30th anniversary of the vaunted GEL Kayano franchise. A revised toggle lacing system secures the upper, crafted from dark green mesh with glossy synthetic overlays in black and Bottle Green. In addition to co-branded sockliners, the lateral heel of each shoe displays mismatched ‘UNAFFECTED’ and ‘GEL Kayano 14’ branding. The lifestyle runner is mounted on a lightweight EVA midsole with GEL cushioning for improved comfort and impact protection.

attributes.name: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Unaffected Infinite Wonders Pack Black Silver
attributes.story: The UNAFFECTED x ASICS GEL Kayano 14 ‘Dark Shadow’ is taken from the ‘Infinite Wonders Pack,’ a three-piece footwear collection designed in partnership with the South Korean brand. A toggle lacing system secures the upper, built with dark grey mesh and synthetic overlays in black and metallic silver. Dual branding appears on the insoles, while ‘UNAFFECTED’ and ‘GEL Kayano 14’ are stamped on the lateral heel of each shoe. The lifestyle runner rests on a lightweight EVA midsole with visible GEL cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

attributes.name: ASICS Gel-Kayano 14 Unaffected Infinite Wonders Pack White
attributes.story: Launching as part of the collaborative ‘Infinite Wonders Pack,’ the UNAFFECTED x ASICS GEL Kayano 14 ‘Bright White’ updates the lifestyle runner with a modified design inspired by the great outdoors. Toggle lacing secures the upper, crafted from white mesh with tonal synthetic overlays. Contrasting black accents land on the ASICS tongue patch and heel overlay, marked with mismatched GEL Kayano 14 and UNAFFECTED branding on the lateral side of each shoe. The sneaker rides on a lightweight EVA midsole with visible GEL cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

ASICS Gel-Lyte III Up There Kookaburra
attributes.story: The Up There x ASICS Gel Lyte 3 ‘Kookaburra’ takes inspiration from a laughing bird species native to Australia. The colors of the ‘scruffy larrikin’ are mirrored in the design of the upper, featuring an off-white mesh base with blue leather side stripes on the lateral side. Arrayed across a midfoot leather overlay, brown speckling becomes increasingly dense, transitioning to suede paneling in a solid dark brown finish. Inside the shoe, custom insoles display a kookaburra graphic, along with dual Up There and ASICS branding.

ASICS GT-2160 Above The Clouds
attributes.story: The Above The Clouds x ASICS GT 2160 ‘Shamrock Green’ reunites the creative partners on a lifestyle running shoe that made its original debut in 2011. The mixed-material upper features translucent NEXKIN throughout the vamp and midfoot, along with white open-cell mesh around the collar and heel. Metallic silver side stripes are outlined in green trim, matching the eyelets, interior lining and reinforced toe. Custom insoles display ASICS and Above The Clouds branding. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a sculpted EVA midsole with visible GEL inserts in the heel.
